Elliott Management Corporation Key Developments

Elliott Mulls Offer For Oncor Electric
Jul 12 17
Elliott Management Corporation (Elliott‘) is considering the acquisition of Oncor Electric Delivery Company, LLC for $18.5 billion, Wall Street Journal informed. The terms offered by Elliott could be better than the $18 billion submitted by Berkshire Hathaway Energy Company.


Elliott To Reportedly Acquire Stake In STADA
Jul 6 17
Elliott Management Corporation is said to build STADA Arzneimittel Aktiengesellschaft (DB:SAZ) stake amid bids. Elliott owns more than 5% of Stada and could disclose the stake as soon as this week.


Elliott Management Corporation Presents at Bloomberg L.P. Inaugural Invest New York Summit 2017, Jun-07-2017 03:40 PM
Jun 3 17
Elliott Management Corporation Presents at Bloomberg L.P. Inaugural Invest New York Summit 2017, Jun-07-2017 03:40 PM. Venue: Bloomberg HQ, New York, New York, United States. Speakers: Paul Elliott Singer, Chief Executive Officer, President, Co-Chief Investment Officer, Senior Risk Manager, and Director.


